name: NESTED_FORM_COMPONENT
description: This table contains information about the nested form components used in hemodynamic data entry templates. These include sets, subsets, fields, and field components. This table contains the information about components that does not change overtime.

columns.name: FORM_COMP_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the component record.

columns.name: NESTCOMP_NAME
columns.description: The record name for the component.
